ruck is a simple scrum project management tool.  There's more of a description on my website at http://neidetcher.com/ruck.html .

If you understand scrum you should be able to use it right away.

The license is GPLv3.  We implemented it in Grails.  

demian0311@gmail.com
johnnywey@gmail.com

To run it with the in-memory database:
grails run-app

To run it using a MySQL database on localhost named 'ruck' with a user 'ruck' and password 'ruck'.
grails prod run-app